# CryptoRPG

CryptoRPG is a tiny barebones RPG for players to interact with during Twitch streams.

## Features

- Check for coins every 5 minutes
- Fight monsters every 5 minutes
- Check and buy from a shared shop

Each user has 4 stats

- STR
- MAG
- DEF
- SPR

These stats wil allow users to beat stronger enemies and gain bigger prizes
